{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述黑衣人（疑似南宫丑）深夜借宿郭大路住处。他沉默寡言，举止怪异，站着睡觉如柱子般冷硬。燕七和王动对其身份产生猜测。随后\"恶鸟\"康同率四名外门兵器高手潜入，欲夺取催命符赃物。绿衫鬼公子现身，以折扇轻松击杀四人，手段残忍。鬼公子与黑衣人对峙，双方言语交锋后动手。黑衣人以奇特身法拔出六尺寒机剑，一剑穿透柱子刺死鬼公子。次日黑衣人悄然离去，郭大路感叹遇上了可怕人物，燕七则担忧这神秘剑客会带来更大麻烦。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫丑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必等了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里既不便，我也不勉强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下真请我进去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的，请进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不后悔？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你从来不喝酒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么时候才喝？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀过人后。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么样说来，你还是不要喝酒的好。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后面有客房，你既然不喝酒，就请过去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必？不必干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必去客房。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道就睡在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然要睡在这里，为什么不躺下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必躺下？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马不会说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但只有马才站着睡觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是匹马？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫丑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像南宫丑这种人，若没有目的，怎么会到这里来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么不能来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么要来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论哪一种人，晚上都要找个地方睡觉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真认为他是来睡觉的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他正在睡觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论他为的是什么，他现在总是在睡觉，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们大家都应该去睡觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么还不去睡？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想看看，他是不是真的睡着了，能睡多久？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这是我的房间，我要睡了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你睡你的，我又不会吵你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不行？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有别人在我屋里，我睡不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为世上只有两种人不娶老婆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪两种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为他是先到这里来卧底的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，真奇怪。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事奇怪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你身上为什么一点也不臭？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能不能不臭？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁就更臭了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来他们并不是同路的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来这些人也不是一路来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地盘是我们的，我们不出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我生怕他们打扰了你的清梦，已打发了他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非你已知道他们要来，所以先在这里等着他们？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不配。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这些人的确不配你出手，那么你是在等谁呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承蒙你看得起，真是荣幸之至。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在这里既然等我的，莫非已知道我的来意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们以前也见过面，彼此一直都很客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只要问这里的主人几句话，立刻就走。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只问两句。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然不是，你和我一样，从来都没有朋友的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然不是朋友，你为什么要管这闲事呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已管了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非你也在跟我打一样的主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不会滚。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不滚就死！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "鬼公子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁死谁活也还不一定，你又何必要出手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才这里发生过什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才这里难道什么都没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你最好莫要多想，想多了反而烦恼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又答对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为这件事无论你想不想，都一样会有烦恼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么烦恼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去问问他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我无论有什么大大小小的毛病，一喝酒就好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你是不是也想喝两杯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？你刚才不是已经……已经杀过人了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我杀过人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才你杀的那……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不是人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不是人？要什么样的才能算是人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世上的人很少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我呢？能不能算是人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我杀你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里没有贼赃，这里什么都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你为什么来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "错过宿头，来借宿一宵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是刚才你却为这件事杀了那个不是人的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是为这件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是为了我们杀他的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要睡了，我睡的时候，不喜欢别人打扰。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想我实在很走运。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 841,
      "line_end": 841
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走运？为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 843,
      "line_end": 843
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我上次遇见的那黑衣人，不是这个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 845,
      "line_end": 845
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这次你还是遇见了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 847,
      "line_end": 847
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 853,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 855
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你儿子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 857,
      "line_end": 857
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若有这么样一个儿子，不发疯也差不多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 859,
      "line_end": 859
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为天下真有这么样的好人好事？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 865,
      "line_end": 865
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的意思，是不是说他一定还另有目的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 867,
      "line_end": 867
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 869,
      "line_end": 869
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的目的是什么呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 871,
      "line_end": 871
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 873,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 879,
      "line_end": 879
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想这麻烦什么时候会来呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 881,
      "line_end": 881
    }
